voices.mp3Text: My purpose is clear, my targets doomed.
I am the pride of Nyx.
As the chosen assassin of the greatest goddess Nyx, I can promise you that this one's in the bag.
My purpose is clear, my targets doomed.
I have one purpose for being.
My words enter the mind, but not the ear.
The better to kill them with.
I am the pride of Nyx.
Ahaha, another body laid to waste.
You are as dead as they come.
Go the way of all flesh.
I hear your thoughts no more.
Heheahah ahaha haha, Nyx, Nyx, Nyx.
For you, dear Nyx, for you.
Nyx, Nyx, Nyx, heh heh hah.
Ahahah, Nyx, Nyx, Nyx, Nyx, Nyx, heh heh.
Neither hot, nor cold, just dead.
I silence one voice, then the other.
Your metamorphosis was impressive, I will admit.
Not an easy bug to kill, but worth the effort.
Caught in your own web, ahe.
Your exoskeleton was no match for Nyx.
The ogre and his parasite are no more.
The stealth assassin, not stealthy enough.
Your books couldn't save you, Warlock.
Hahahaha! Your books couldn't save you.
May the silverfish devour your books.
Ah, the insects can feast on your corpse.
It seems the insects have been eating you for some time already.
Your life without end comes to an end.
Hehehe, you fought well, for a keen.
I despised you since the birth of my whole entire caste.
First blood, heheah hah heh! Nyx, Nyx.
In the name of Nyx, the first assassination is complete!
Come, we will spin them into death, Broodmother.
Ah, impressive stinger Sand King. Very sharp, yes.
Earth shall shake, I shall kill.
You must earn Nyx's grace, Lion.
What use have I for coin?
Your bribe of coin is wasted on Nyx.
You can't run from your thoughts.
No, no, no, heh heh, hah.
Th, a tool of the trade.
Long has this been in my thoughts.
Another will rise in my place.
With my last thought, I curse you.
I have failed the goddess Nyx.
I am Nyx, grakillaaghraamghiah! Oi-grayoighaaah… Nyx-aaaagh…
The ogre and his parasite slay me.
Write my name in the book of the dead.
It's always darkest before the spawn.
My thoughts cohere from the ether.
The chosen of Nyx knows not failure.
There is always a Nyx assassin.
The new Nyx assassin is risen.
Oh, they're going to hate this.
We all look alike to you.

voices.mp3Text: Armorless beings were not meant for life.
Many are the soldiers, workers and reproductives of my colony. But I am the fourth caste. The assassin caste. The caste of one.
I could have been a lowly grub, but by the grace of our goddess Nyx, I have been elevated to the highest state. Nor shall I disappoint her.
The blessing of Nyx gives me all the purpose I require.
It is not my fault. The armorless were not meant for life. Look at them.
Ahahah, Nyx, Nyx, Nyx, Nyx, Nyx, heh heh.
Oh, great Nyx, your assassin's life has been fulfilled.
Nyx has no use for me now.
Ah, Nyx favors me with a gift.
